---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Privacy Policy | Mortgage Calculator" description="Review the privacy policy for Mortgage Calculator. We do not store, track, or sell your personal financial calculations." page="privacy">

<div class="hero" style="max-width: 800px; padding-bottom: 3rem;">
  <h1>Privacy <strong>Policy</strong></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub" style="max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Your financial calculations are your business. Learn how we handle your data.</p>
</div>

<section style="padding: 0 0 5rem;">
  <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; background: var(--surf); border: 1px solid var(--bd); border-radius: var(--rl); padding: 3rem 2.5rem; box-shadow: var(--sh);">
    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink3); margin-bottom: 2rem;">Last Updated: June 20, 2025</p>

    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 1rem;">1. Data Collection</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">We do not collect, store, or transmit any of the financial figures or inputs you enter into our calculators (including income, home price, down payment, or debts). All calculations are executed locally in your browser using JavaScript. Once you close the tab, all inputs are wiped.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">2. Cookies & Third-Party Advertising</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">We use Google AdSense to serve advertisements on our site. Google uses cookies (specifically the DoubleClick cookie) to serve ads based on your visit to this website and other sites on the internet. You can opt out of personalized advertising by visiting Google's Ads Settings.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">3. Web Analytics</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">We may use anonymous analytics tools (like Google Analytics) to track page visits, click rates, and general referral traffic to improve user experiences. No personally identifiable information (PII) is captured during this process.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">4. Third-Party Links</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Our website contains links to outside resources (such as our parent agency website, Social Ninja's). We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party websites.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">5. Contact Us</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 15px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.75;">If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="https://socialninjas.in/contact" target="_blank" style="color: var(--blue); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">socialninjas.in/contact</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>
